tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ai_ethical_guidelines (
  guideline_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  guideline_name VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  created_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE ethical_guidelines (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    principle_text TEXT,
    guideline_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE implementation_guidelines (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    guideline_title VARCHAR(255),
    guideline_text TEXT,
    suggested_actions TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE development_process (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    process_name VARCHAR(255),
    process_description TEXT,
    tools_and_frameworks TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE stakeholders (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stakeholder_name VARCHAR(255),
    stakeholder_type VARCHAR(50),
    contact_information TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ai_ethical_guidelines (
  guideline_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  guideline_name VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  issue_date DATE,
  compliance_status BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE ai_principles (
  principle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  principle_name VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ai_applications (
  application_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  application_name VARCHAR(255),
  description TEXT,
  development_stage VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE ai_impact (
  impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  impact_description TEXT,
  affected_stakeholders TEXT,
  mitigation_strategy TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ai_ethics_review (
  review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  guideline_id INT,
  reviewer_name VARCHAR(255),
  review_date DATE,
  review_result BOOLEAN
)
